<!-- Main hero unit for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
<div class="hero-unit">
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p><%= name %> is an infinite virtual corkboard.  Collaborate with friends, family, or colleagues in real time 
    in any way you want. Make plans, share ideas, play games...</p>
    <p>This is a free service (please donate to help cover costs) and the code will be open sourced very soon. Please feel 
    free to make suggestions for improvements and let us know about any of those nasty bugs.</p>
    <p><a href="/create" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get started &raquo;</a> Click this bad boy to create your first board</p>
</div>

<!-- Example row of columns -->
<div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p><%= name %> is an infinite virtual corkboard which can be put to use in many different ways!</p>
        <p>Best of all <%= name %> is open source so you are welcome to make improvements to the system or run your 
        own instance. </p>
        <p>We're currently still in <strong>alpha</strong> but hope to improve the system over the coming weeks and get 
        a stable product out there. In the meantime please feel free to use and 
        <a href="https://github.com/pinittome/pinitto.me/issues" target="_blank">let us know about any problems</a>.</p>
        <p><a class="btn" href="/about">About &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h2>Statistics</h2>
        <p>Some real time stats about what is going on with the system:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Number of boards: <span class="totals-boards"><%=totals.boards %></span></li>
            <li>Number of cards: <span class="totals-cards"><%=totals.cards %></span></li>
        </ul>
        <p><a class="btn disabled" href="#">Realtime statistics &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <% if (typeof(twitter) !== 'undefined') { %>
    <div class="span4">
        <h2>Twitter</h2>
        <div class="tweet"></div>
        <p><a class="btn" href="https://twitter.com/<%=twitter %>" target="_blank">Follow us &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <% } %>
</div>

<hr>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; Company 2013</p>
</footer>